{"tid":1062101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔怪得俾人打尖","createTime":"2019-03-15T01:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T09:20:46.000Z","uid":138803,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de20ad1401a64efd26932f1008d633c60543f9e3","tid":1062101,"uid":138803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:03:51.000Z","msg":"頭先有對拖住行李嘅大陸人情侶<br />\n喺過海巴士線打尖<br />\n仲要扮無知 話冇事嘅<br />\n我用普通話講排隊後面<br />\n兇一兇佢真係行咗去<br />\n點知我10幾個人後面再打尖<br />\n但根本冇人理<br />\n點解咁唔爭氣<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得啲大陸人打尖當食生菜<br />\n根本上冇人理<br />\n等佢地覺得打尖好正常/香港人好易呃<br />\n到其他事情上面蝕底都好似正常<br />\n或者當面又唔敢話佢地<br />\n唔好做鍵盤戰士喇<br />\n爭氣啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd41a5d7b647ee173bf5fcee0d65d76cc07f9e7c","tid":1062101,"uid":240055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:07:37.000Z","msg":"十幾個咪少囉，我試過屌撚完佢，佢行後1個再插過，照樣無人出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b275362532a4d937c98a223ebe4bb0fad172c18","tid":1062101,"uid":138803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd41a5d7b647ee173bf5fcee0d65d76cc07f9e7c","tid":1062101,"uid":240055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:07:37.000Z","msg":"十幾個咪少囉，我試過屌撚完佢，佢行後1個再插過，照樣無人出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:08:49.000Z","msg":"我就冇好惡咁講<br />\n語氣好平靜<br />\n佢可能良心發現先排遠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82e80675e01be493d43c14cdb9dda99c24fb523","tid":1062101,"uid":240055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd41a5d7b647ee173bf5fcee0d65d76cc07f9e7c","tid":1062101,"uid":240055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:07:37.000Z","msg":"十幾個咪少囉，我試過屌撚完佢，佢行後1個再插過，照樣無人出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:10:52.000Z","msg":"多先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a077af299b7655cef30d7339dcabc5082b1db20","tid":1062101,"uid":34514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:22:28.000Z","msg":"香港人對住大陸人打尖就係咁，係網上凶神惡煞，但係現實就鵪鶉咁。"},{"pid":"51c6dc2019ae65f13927bf4b0086d4d321dd61d8","tid":1062101,"uid":138803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a077af299b7655cef30d7339dcabc5082b1db20","tid":1062101,"uid":34514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:22:28.000Z","msg":"香港人對住大陸人打尖就係咁，係網上凶神惡煞，但係現實就鵪鶉咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:00:44.000Z","msg":"其實都唔使好弱咁講嘅<br />\n正常tone先係最好"},{"pid":"5d7caa8b5497a47a11c0954969d9f60973d6b970","tid":1062101,"uid":85787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:04:25.000Z","msg":"有時佢地一支火箭咁衝左上去，又真係好難捉返佢落嚟。。。"},{"pid":"c3bf4c93a6efc0249004d0daa62591e6c43a4fd8","tid":1062101,"uid":229183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d82baa4f251454f79759f3c00977705e8f8b06","tid":1062101,"uid":138803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d7caa8b5497a47a11c0954969d9f60973d6b970","tid":1062101,"uid":85787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:04:25.000Z","msg":"有時佢地一支火箭咁衝左上去，又真係好難捉返佢落嚟。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"今日落樓梯嗰時插隊<br />\n個個玩手機就俾人乘虛而入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}